{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8022f7a4e0","title":"中央、中央文革首长接见西藏班部分学员时的重要指示","origin":"西藏自治区革命委员会汇编：《中央、中央文革关于西藏无产阶级文化大革命的重要指示》，1968年9月。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"670756f2da","index":0,"year":1968,"month":8,"day":26,"articleId":"8022f7a4e0"}],"tags":[{"id":"0a84ea94c2","name":"二月逆流","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"0b2012c0b4","name":"革命三结合","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"0b6d8a885e","name":"革命委员会","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"0faca0c469","name":"张国华","type":"人物"},{"id":"1ae024ca96","name":"革命大联合","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"3457e40c94","name":"党内资产阶级","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"40ffd466ef","name":"武斗","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"75e62558d2","name":"清理阶级队伍","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"82305e518c","name":"江青","type":"人物"},{"id":"82c2346f26","name":"江苏文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"92a8a42842","name":"姚文元","type":"人物"},{"id":"aa9434abe4","name":"北京文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"cb4c84f4c0","name":"西藏文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"ef71f03227","name":"中央文革","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"82350694e4","type":"title","text":"中央、中央文革首长接见西藏班部分学员时的重要指示","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"105a15ee0b","type":"subtitle","text":"（记录稿，未经首长审阅）","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"5fe27270bb","type":"paragraph","text":"时间：1968年8月26日23点15分至27日凌晨2点35分。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"5a9a198ac5","type":"paragraph","text":"地点：人民大会堂东大厅。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"2652a9f4ae","type":"paragraph","text":"参加接见的首长有：总理、陈伯达、康生、江青、姚文元、谢富治、黄永胜、吴法宪、叶群、汪东兴、温玉成。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"64798600bb","type":"paragraph","text":"当中央、中央文革首长进入大厅时，全体起立，热烈鼓掌，高呼“毛主席万岁！万岁！万万岁！”“祝毛主席万寿无疆！万寿无疆！万寿无疆”“祝林副主席身体健康！永远健康！永远健康！”","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"9ddd7b51c6","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：同志们好！好久就想见你们了，对不起同志们，你们等了很久。今天开会主要听听同志们的意见，希望同志们有什么意见告诉中央，同时，希望你们两派很快联合起来成立革命委员会，你们不一定是最后一个，还大有希望。今天是8月26号了，要只争朝夕，争取8月份成立就好了。请同志们谈谈。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"9095dd059c","type":"paragraph","text":"姚文元同志：谁先谈？","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"2ab89e91f0","type":"paragraph","text":"（陶长松同志：我发言。）","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"91d540a49b","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：叫什么名字？哪一派的？","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"22b63f40d5","type":"paragraph","text":"（陶答：“造总”。）","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"84230c2d73","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：那里人？（答：江苏人）学什么的？（答：学中文的）教什么的？（答：汉语）","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"29126be53f","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：江苏人到那里去了。","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"23eb7298b8","type":"paragraph","text":"（当陶汇报到两派揪斗了一百多名叛徒、特务、走资派时）","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"7e10ec1ba3","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：是两派内部的，还是外部的？","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"7735ddb776","type":"paragraph","text":"（当陶汇报到汉商问题时）","index":15,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"95390be856","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：什么时候去的？有多少？","index":16,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"ae26a2fb2e","type":"paragraph","text":"（当陶汇报到尼商问题时）","index":17,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"510ec53446","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：不单是尼泊尔，还有锡金、不丹吧！","index":18,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"90cc72aea6","type":"paragraph","text":"（当陶谈到对军队问题时）","index":19,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"adf2621be8","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：那时就有两派？（总理笑着对康老讲，两派都去支持，他们还不要哩！）","index":20,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"5da89f89bc","type":"paragraph","text":"（当陶汇报到抢了一百多支枪时）","index":21,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"55234cb79a","type":"paragraph","text":"总理、江青（笑）：太少了。当然抢枪是不对的。","index":22,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"b1f846ac07","type":"paragraph","text":"文元：“造总”实际有多少人？","index":23,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"f43eb5033a","type":"paragraph","text":"（陶：各地报的有20万）（中央首长笑了）","index":24,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"5d3840a14b","type":"paragraph","text":"（当陶检查到运动初期对待张国华同志有错误时说，听了小道消息，说他参加了二月兵变）","index":25,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"e02476f664","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：那里来的小道消息？（陶：到现在我们也还没有弄清楚）","index":26,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"a15e6648bf","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：是从北京传去的。","index":27,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"17814e19eb","type":"paragraph","text":"（当陶谈到“造总”有人参加黑会问题时）","index":28,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"83c16f13c3","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：（笑）想搞些小道消息。","index":29,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"0558cf9904","type":"paragraph","text":"（当陶汇报到“专打”整了张国华的材料，也有张经武的材料时）","index":30,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"5a3aff5b07","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：张经武那时还没有发现。","index":31,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"0c53b581ea","type":"paragraph","text":"（当陶汇报到大联合问题时，说拉萨市还没有联合。赵文贵同志插话：拉萨市今天已达成了革命大联合协议）","index":32,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"b111d568a8","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：（带头鼓掌）好！","index":33,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"8a8a792b12","type":"paragraph","text":"（当陶汇报到2、3月问题、平反工作还未解决，还不落实，如有的工资还没发时）","index":34,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"2bc4d7c4d7","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：任荣同志，还有没发工资的吗？（任答：可能有，已经发过通知了，要发。）应该发。","index":35,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"ab4dbd5be1","type":"paragraph","text":"（当陶希望中央对二月逆流平反工作有个明确指示时）","index":36,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"57c3f47edd","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：早就明确指示了。","index":37,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"ef262d88e4","type":"paragraph","text":"（刘绍民同志发言）","index":38,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"2465b24516","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：叫什么名字？（答：刘绍民）那一边的？（答：“大联指”）过去在公安厅工作吗？（答：区党委办公厅）","index":39,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"894abe5659","type":"paragraph","text":"（当刘汇报到抢了人民解放军的枪时）","index":40,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"6c0e766617","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：到底是抢的，还是送的枪？还是明抢暗送？（刘答：是抢的）","index":41,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"d89c0c308b","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们抢得容易些。（刘绍民答：我们不打解放军）","index":42,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"fdd3e2fb9c","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：部队里边你们观点的多些，你们抢起来便当些。","index":43,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"69c020018a","type":"paragraph","text":"（当刘汇报到防止骄傲时）","index":44,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"0887001728","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：你们两派里边有没有坏人？（刘答：肯定有）具体讲你们这一派有没有？你们有没有揪出几个来？","index":45,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"1e0b71142d","type":"paragraph","text":"防止骄傲，防止犯错误，最重要的一条是把阶级队伍清理好，把坏人揪出来，这是最重要的一条。","index":46,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"f9f1ec73e0","type":"paragraph","text":"（朱景尚同志汇报）","index":47,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"f1bd6dcf35","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：“大联指”参加北京黑会了没有？（刘答：没有）","index":48,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"8658a26b7a","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：这里我要向“大联指”说一句话，我们要向你们解释一下，你们不能因为“造总”有人参加黑会就抓人家小辫子。这个会是很复杂的，我们了解过，参加会的各方面情况都不一样，“造总”主要是军区压它，要去诉苦，找几个同情的，是听听情况的，他们同那些别有用心的人不是一回事的，也是可以理解的。","index":49,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"4ab410b83a","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：同广东、广西、北京的不一样。","index":50,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"1b0693d82d","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：如果你们换个位置、换个条件，假如你们在那种情况下，你们也会去的。他们已检查了是好的，你们不要认为他们参加了就犯了大错误，你们没去，就不要认为你们就高明。","index":51,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"4d00985905","type":"paragraph","text":"（当朱景尚谈到拉萨打冷枪时）","index":52,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"a7af65375f","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：这几天是不是好些了？（陈明义：好些了）","index":53,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"f8af20b681","type":"paragraph","text":"（丁一德同志要求发言）","index":54,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"ec0180a53a","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：叫藏族同志说说。","index":55,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"aa3d18d935","type":"paragraph","text":"永胜：让藏族同志讲讲好。","index":56,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"27d4cccb1a","type":"paragraph","text":"（热地同志发言）","index":57,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"27d5ba1fce","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：那派的？（答：“大联指”那曲总司）什么名字？（答：热地）（那曲总司张清法同志插话）","index":58,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"2b43bf7165","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你怎么插他的话？","index":59,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"87bf32e078","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：还是让他讲完。","index":60,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"fc2423a6e5","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：汉族同志要注意发挥藏族同志的积极性。（对刘绍民、陶长松）藏族来得太少了。","index":61,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"79a19ce3ef","type":"paragraph","text":"（丁一德同志发言。当汇报到对方还不承认“造总”时）","index":62,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"0ee9175a42","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：他们不是承认你们了吗？热地不是刚才向你们赔礼道歉了吗？","index":63,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"5ce22b3f3f","type":"paragraph","text":"文元：还是要向前看。","index":64,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"97b8c0e934","type":"paragraph","text":"（当丁汇报到那曲中层干部成立“挺身而出战斗队”时）","index":65,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"e280ebfa39","type":"paragraph","text":"文元：这个组织现在还有没有？","index":66,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"d05ebd46aa","type":"paragraph","text":"（当丁汇报到那曲的革筹委调查研究组在三教运动期间抓了1400多个反革命的情况时）","index":67,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"a0ef698d2a","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：我不知道这件事。","index":68,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"6ef5360ab5","type":"paragraph","text":"（当丁汇报到那曲原地委书记又在革筹掌权时）","index":69,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"a11af0d952","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：现在掌权的这个人叫什么名字？（答：张夺锦）是什么地方人？（答：河北赵县）是随军进藏的吗？","index":70,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"8377f489f0","type":"paragraph","text":"（陈明义答：不是的，河南调去的）","index":71,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"a251619636","type":"paragraph","text":"（其他专县同志纷纷要求发言）","index":72,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"8c860e7d05","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：关于部分的问题你们相互协商。现在情况和过去不同了，大家要向前看。摆在我们面前是如何联合起来，团结起来成立革委会。我提出两个问题：","index":73,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"cd5e188044","type":"paragraph","text":"一个问题：西藏军区党委会、军管会向中央提出革委会的报告，你们看了没有，讨论过没有？","index":74,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"791700560d","type":"paragraph","text":"（有的说看到了，有的说没有看到，有的说讨论了，有的说没有。共同的反映没有认真讨论，修改后没有看过）","index":75,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"72267362a3","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：不管人数多少，时间长短，你们文件应该交给他们。","index":76,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"4eda32103a","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：应该讨论，酝酿。","index":77,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"8b6f2a8ff3","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：名单是不是你们两派都同意的？比如主任、副主任是不是都同意。","index":78,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"1db33387e6","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：把军区的检查和成立革委会的报告都应该给他们讨论。军区七八个常委都分头下去听听你们的意见。如果你们没有时间印，我们连夜给你们印300份，每人一份，明天早晨7点钟你们讨论。","index":79,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"06d240c7a0","type":"paragraph","text":"（当几个人同时站起来要求发言）","index":80,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"aac763c255","type":"paragraph","text":"总理、康老：都是“造总”的，“造总”意见多些哟。","index":81,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"03b92c976d","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：已经大联合了，要合在一起讨论嘛，不要这一派讨论那一派讨论。","index":82,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"805587f6ec","type":"paragraph","text":"（当刘士毅对革委会主任、副主任的人选提出意见时）","index":83,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"dc30c93a32","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：你们讨论时再一起研究。","index":84,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"370914ad43","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：我听了有个感觉，“大联指”是多数派，“造总”相对的是少数派，一直受压，“大联指”更要姿态高点，都是革命群众组织，要搞革命大联合，搞三结合，联合起来可以揪斗坏人，团结起来对付一小撮阶级敌人。（对刘绍民）我有个感觉，“大联指”似乎有点耿耿于怀。","index":85,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"cf21ae49cc","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：“造总”的态度还是好的。","index":86,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"9b3a2c64a8","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：要为革命，要为无产阶级文化大革命站在毛主席革命路线上搞革命大联合。军队也是这样。","index":87,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"9ca7447e0a","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：“大联指”要注意这个问题，去年2、3月“造总”被抓了人，被镇压，“大联指”没有被抓人，应当理解他们，同情他们。","index":88,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"05e8dfde9d","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：四川搞了个“镇反”运动。二月逆流是不能翻案的！确确实实是搞复辟的。","index":89,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"d1e3edfa4a","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：你们“大联指”应该深刻理解，不能拿8、9月“偏保”去同2、3月对消，不能并摆，你们没被抓人，它是受镇压了嘛。","index":90,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"d31bb74b92","type":"paragraph","text":"文元：这个上次已经讲过了，互相多作自我批评。","index":91,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"0959f6c778","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：（对刘绍民）你们是受军队一派捧（宠）上天去的，军队也分派。康老讲过，“大联指”要防止骄傲，翘尾巴。对二月逆流是个什么东西你们不清楚。二月逆流是反革命复辟，这个案是翻不了的！这个时候镇反是不对的，革命小将、革命群众、干部运动中犯错误是难免的。你们不能把错误掩盖下来，应该吸取经验教训，双方多作自我批评，在这里，“大联指”更应多作自我批评，不能以多数压少数。（黄金澄领呼“毛主席万岁”等口号）双方都各自找自己的缺点，“造总”也不要以为“大联指”同志压了我们，反过来对“大联指”怎么样怎么样。双方多作自我批评，达到大联合的目的。今天我是打遭遇战，有一段时间感冒了，听了军区的汇报也没有弄清楚，今天听了你们的意见，才听清楚了。所以还是应该向前看，过去有人在背后搞鬼。两派都是革命群众组织嘛。","index":92,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"719a700427","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：这里我插一句，军队同志，抓的人凡不是叛徒、特务，要勇敢的改，应该彻底地给他们平反，这一点要明确，不能拖拖拉拉，不能含糊。","index":93,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"a0a2829aa9","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：不能拖拉。","index":94,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"2dade9cf2e","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：警司副司令、政委被打，被关，到底他们对不对，是不是反革命？（对军区首长）你们态度怎么样？","index":95,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"ba74236fed","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：6月7号派队伍就是错误的，没经中央同意，军区常委承认了错误。冯锦国同志来了吗？为什么不叫他来？","index":96,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"7cd5f64335","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：有两个月不给送电，中央最近才知道。（刘绍民：报社5月份被打了3次，给打出来）","index":97,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"dbefb61f87","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：已停止武斗了。（刘绍民：不仅在西藏打，还在内地发通令！）","index":98,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"dc612ac690","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：（对刘绍民）你是报馆的吗？（答：不是）你们报馆一年多没出报了。","index":99,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"bd2ebf6cfa","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：“大联指”一个派报发到连队3个月，党报、军报没有了，这是什么问题？","index":100,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"626e7dafbf","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：革命委员会快成立了，报纸还没有出来，象个什么样子！你们联合了没有？什么时候出报？（孔庆贵：这我们要检查）","index":101,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"2cff8718f8","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：把报纸办起来。","index":102,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"29379787c6","type":"paragraph","text":"文元：各省成立革委会都是出了报纸的。","index":103,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"db22890865","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：报馆的工人同志要起领导作用。","index":104,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"d1cf79ac99","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：杨炳来了没有？联合没联合出报？（杨答：3月份就联合出报……）","index":105,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"82208d03c5","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：什么时候啦！你3月8月也弄不清。","index":106,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"3740f059ba","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：杨炳，你要负责啊，你是编辑嘛。","index":107,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"9b9f91502d","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：（对孔庆贵）不要讲了，看什么时候出报！","index":108,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"3e034714a4","type":"paragraph","text":"文元：先出电讯稿。","index":109,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"2f5275d98a","type":"paragraph","text":"（当杨汉青讲我们无条件联合出报时）","index":110,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"e966190047","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：好嘛。","index":111,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"ac7c4cbea9","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：出报还有什么条件！就是传达毛主席的声音嘛。","index":112,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"1da989153d","type":"paragraph","text":"（当孔庆贵提出回报社出报安全没保证时）","index":113,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"efe63578e2","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：你们说没有保证，十一师不是有一个连在报社吗？你们要相信人民解放军嘛。十一师来人了吗？","index":114,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"71db383fc1","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：（对郑万兴）康老问你，能不能保证，你们派了一个连住报社，要支持他们大联合。（郑：我们尽最大努力保证）","index":115,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"5aabb61ce6","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：（指成立革委会报告和军区检查）先给大家讨论，然后再报中央。","index":116,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"9af06332ac","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：先小组讨论，人不多，不难嘛。","index":117,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"718be08e41","type":"paragraph","text":"文元：革委会成立，中央要出一篇社论祝贺你们，你们不出报连社论也没有地方登。","index":118,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"9e433449db","type":"paragraph","text":"（当达瓦汇报到要求解决“六·七”事件死者的抚恤问题，要求彻底收交枪时）","index":119,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"6c0cbc2db6","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：这个同志讲的好！（江青同志带头鼓掌）在大召寺死去的同胞，党、政府、军区都要解决，按国家规定进行抚恤，要把仇恨集中在阶级敌人身上。","index":120,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"a75587e0ce","type":"paragraph","text":"（当达瓦汇报到要求中央把西藏达赖、班禅的残渣余孽及混入两派的坏人都揪出来时）","index":121,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"b3efd78c2a","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：对！联合起来，清理阶级队伍。（伯达同志带头鼓掌）","index":122,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"340c9788c2","type":"paragraph","text":"文元：大联合以后，坏人就逃不掉了。","index":123,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"51e3b9d08a","type":"paragraph","text":"（当达瓦讲到他做梦也没想到会幸福地来到北京，见到了伟大领袖毛主席，见到了敬爱的中央首长时）","index":124,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"3590335665","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：讲的好！谢谢你！（众呼口号：向江青同志学习！致敬！）","index":125,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"dd332eb28e","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：向同志们致敬！向同志们学习！","index":126,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"5d605adb65","type":"paragraph","text":"（当拉珍要求发言时）","index":127,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"e0e0621627","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：拉珍同志，见见面，今天不要讲了，以后还有机会，你喊几句口号吧。","index":128,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"04fb842202","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：散会。","index":129,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"975e7067c6","type":"paragraph","text":"最后，总理叫达瓦、拉珍到前边和中央首长一一握手告别。","index":130,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"d9dbf2c195","type":"paragraph","text":"高呼：“毛主席万岁”等革命口号。","index":131,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"},{"id":"7931f1217f","type":"paragraph","text":"高唱《大海航行靠舵手》","index":132,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0"}],"page":{"id":"4f053a60b2","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8022f7a4e0","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}